      <title>泰国新任卫生部长表示重新考虑大麻非刑事化政策</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/new-thai-health-minister-signals-rethink-of-cannabis-decriminalization-policy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国新任卫生部长表示，他计划审查该国的大麻政策，这表明泰国成为亚洲第一个将大麻合法化的国家后，可能会出现大转变，使大麻再次成为麻醉品。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/new-thai-health-minister-signals-rethink-of-cannabis-decriminalization-policy</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 04:06:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国因担心拉法入侵而暂停向以色列运送武器</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/us-paused-weapons-shipment-to-israel-over-rafah-invasion-concern</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名高级政府官员表示，由于担心以色列即将决定对加沙南部城市拉法发动大范围的军事进攻，美国暂停了向以色列运送炸弹，而总统乔·拜登反对这一行动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/us-paused-weapons-shipment-to-israel-over-rafah-invasion-concern</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 04:02:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加纳反 LGBTQ 法之争威胁到 200 亿美元债务交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/ghana-s-feud-over-anti-lgbtq-law-threatens-20-billion-debt-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[如果阿克拉选择继续实施践踏银行反歧视标准的惩罚性法律，世界银行将面临融资困境。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/ghana-s-feud-over-anti-lgbtq-law-threatens-20-billion-debt-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 04:01:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>犯罪及其对经济造成的 400 亿美元损失是南非投票的核心</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/crime-corruption-are-key-issues-at-heart-of-south-african-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日益加剧的不安全和腐败是 5 月 29 日选举前夕的主要担忧，预计选举将迫使非洲人国民大会达成权力分享协议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/crime-corruption-are-key-issues-at-heart-of-south-african-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 04:00:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马斯克正在与欧洲极右翼接触，但选民不太确定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/musk-is-engaging-with-europe-s-far-right-but-voters-aren-t-so-sure</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃隆·马斯克毫不掩饰他对极右翼德国选择党的兴趣。在经历了一系列自我挫折之后，该党能否保持选民的热情尚不明朗。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/musk-is-engaging-with-europe-s-far-right-but-voters-aren-t-so-sure</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>如果英国央行在资产出售上发生转变，亨特可能会获得 100 亿英镑的减税净额</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/boe-shift-on-quantitative-easing-could-save-uk-government-10-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据英国央行披露，如果英国央行停止出售十多年来在量化宽松政策下购买的债券，英国财政大臣杰里米·亨特每年将额外获得 100 亿英镑的减税资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/boe-shift-on-quantitative-easing-could-save-uk-government-10-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
