    <item>
      <title>塑造领导人形象的朝鲜宣传主管去世，享年 94 岁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/north-korea-propaganda-boss-who-shaped-image-of-leaders-dies-at-94</link>
      <description><![CDATA[金基男是一名宣传策划人，他帮助朝鲜家族王朝建立了个人崇拜，该家族自冷战时期建国以来一直统治朝鲜，他去世，享年 94 岁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/north-korea-propaganda-boss-who-shaped-image-of-leaders-dies-at-94</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 02:53:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列逼近拉法，谈判陷入僵局，局势高度紧张</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/israel-edges-into-rafah-with-tensions-high-over-deadlocked-talks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列控制进入埃及的拉法口岸的举动引发了对其最终目标的激烈争论：这是长期威胁入侵加沙南部城市的开始，还是试图向哈马斯施压，要求放宽停火条件以及释放人质？]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/israel-edges-into-rafah-with-tensions-high-over-deadlocked-talks</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 14:31:05 GMT</pubDate>
